# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your credentials.
# The pipeline works without any keys — optional keys unlock extra features.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Optional: OpenAI (enables GPT-4o-mini narrative analysis) ──────────────
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ── Optional: Reddit OAuth2 (higher rate limits than the public JSON API) ──
# Create an app at https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps (select "script")
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret
